In [51]:
import re

cleaned_text = """
Group Name:
Group Number:
Plan Description:

Gated/Non Gated:

BLT Management Inc
11223344
High Plan

Non-Gated
"""

# Define regular expressions for extracting information
regex_patterns = {
    "Group Name": r"Group Name:(.*)",
    "Group Number": r"Group Number:(.*)",
    "Plan Description": r"Plan Description:(.*)",
    "Gated/Non Gated": r"Gated/Non Gated:(.*)"
}

# Initialize variables to store extracted information
extracted_info = {}

# Iterate through the regular expressions and find matches in the cleaned text
for key, pattern in regex_patterns.items():
    match = re.search(pattern, cleaned_text)
    if match:
        extracted_info[key] = match.group(1).strip()

# Format and print the extracted information
for key, value in extracted_info.items():
    print(f"{key}: {value}")

import pandas as pd
keys = []
values = []

for line in lines:
    parts = line.split(':', 1) 
    key = parts[0].strip() + ':'
    value = parts[1].strip() if len(parts) > 1 else ''  
    keys.append(key)
    values.append(value)

df = pd.DataFrame({'Keys': keys, 'Values': values})
df
